    "description": {
      "value": "\r\n<p class=\"source\"><b>Source</b> <a title=\"PZO9410\" href=\"http://www.amazon.com/gp/product/1601252226/ref=as_li_qf_sp_asin_il_tl?ie=UTF8&amp;camp=1789&amp;creative=9325&amp;creativeASIN=1601252226&amp;linkCode=as2&amp;tag=httpwwwd20pfs-20\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">PZO9410</a></p>\r\n<p><b>Price</b> 15 gp</p>\r\n<p>The milk of this vibrant green cactus, when mixed with resins and other ingredients, congeals into sticky, black chunks with an exceedingly sour taste. Though poppy tears comes in several different varieties, it's refined form is both the most potent and expensive type.</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-weight: bold;border-bottom: solid thin\">Effects</p>\r\n<p><b>Type</b> ingested or inhaled; <b>Addiction</b> moderate, <a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/combat#TOC-Fortitude\">Fortitude</a> DC 20; <b>Initial Effect(s)</b> 1 hour; +1d2 <a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/basics-ability-scores/glossary#TOC-Bonus-Alchemical-\">alchemical bonus</a> to <a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/basics-ability-scores/ability-scores#TOC-Strength-Str-\">Strength</a>, -2 penalty on saves against illusions and mind-affecting effects <b>Secondary Effect(s)</b> after 1 hour; 1d2 hours of <a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/conditions#TOC-Fatigued\">fatigue</a> <b>Damage</b> 1d2 <a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/basics-ability-scores/ability-scores#TOC-Constitution-Con-\">Con</a> and 1d2 <a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/basics-ability-scores/ability-scores#TOC-Wisdom-Wis-\">Wis</a> damage</p>\r\n",
